				"path":{
					"overview":"The Path of Kori\nAwakening the Inner Flame\n\"Kori is not power. It is a truth made visible — the answer to who you are when no one watches.\"\n— Wanderer of the Third Flame\nOverview\nKori  (Sigtaara: \"in-energy\") is the living flame carried by all beings of Fir'Gol .\nThough present from birth, it often slumbers deep within the soul, requiring experience, will, and awakening to bring it forth.\n\nThe journey through Kori is personal — shaped by one's essence — and unfolds through six sacred stages, known collectively as The Path of the Inner Flame.\n\nNo two beings walk this path alike, for the flame bends itself to the heart that bears it.\n\nThe Six Stages of Kori\nStage One — Slumber (Ko'Surhul )\n\"The ember unseen.\"\n\nThe default state of most living beings.\nKori lies dormant, its presence unnoticed but ever patient.\nIndividuals live by instinct and mundane strength, unaware of the deeper well within.\nOnly extraordinary emotion, trauma, or discipline can disturb this stillness.\nStage Two — Stirring (Ko'Gornazil )\n\"The first breath in the ashes.\"\n\nMoments of extreme need, crisis, or inspiration cause Kori to quiver within.\nSigns are subtle: a sudden surge of strength, a clarity of thought, a moment of impossible endurance.\nThe individual feels that something more lies beneath their skin — but cannot yet grasp it.\nStage Three — Ignition (Ko'Wokazil )\n\"The first spark.\"\n\nA conscious awakening of Kori occurs.\nThe bearer senses their inner Flame distinctly for the first time.\nAbilities sharpen, instincts strengthen, emotions grow deeper.\nHowever, control is minimal — bursts of Kori may come wildly and unpredictably.\nStage Four — Kindling (Ko'Larkzil )\n\"The steady flame that feeds itself.\"\n\nThrough discipline, meditation, struggle, or joy, the bearer learns to summon and steady Kori.\nThe inner Flame begins to align with the individual's soul:\nThe wrathful may become living storms.\nThe wise may weave subtle, unseen strength.\nThe joyful may radiate resilience and healing.\nKori now evolves in a direction unique to the heart it serves.\nStage Five — Flameweaving (Ko'Yolhak )\n\"The weaving of the living fire.\"\n\nFull mastery of Kori.\nThe Flame is no longer just personal — it can connect with the Kori of others.\nMasters of Flameweaving are said to sense the pulses of nearby life, binding allies in unseen unity or bolstering the spirits of those around them.\nSome describe the sensation as \"hearing the hidden songs of the soul.\"\nStage Six — The Expansion of the Inner (Ko'Vooklazil )\n\"The Flame becomes the Horizon.\"\n\nA legendary state, rarely achieved even among the greatest masters.\nKori expands beyond the limits of body and mind, becoming a living presence within the world itself.\nThose who reach Ko'Vooklazil are said to leave echoes of themselves imprinted upon the land, blessing the soil, the sky, and the hearts of future generations.\nIn this state, self and world no longer exist as separate.\n",
