							"description":"Ko'Larkzil is the fourth stage of the Path of Kori — a crucible of refinement, clarity, and discipline. The inner Flame, once erratic and exhausting, now stabilizes into something enduring. The bearer learns to summon Kori with ease, sustain heightened states without collapse, and begin forging unique expressions of power rooted in personal truth. At this stage, the Flame no longer strains the body with each use. Instead, it rises naturally, like breath, guided by will and tempered by understanding. This is the moment when strength becomes craft. But with that craft comes the obligation to face oneself: to explore emotional wounds, to release illusions, to choose which parts of the soul are worthy of flame. Ko'Larkzil is not about becoming more powerful — it is about becoming more whole.",
